    "The PBRPK would predict the physical dose and secondary risk and also control the pharmacokinetic and injection profile.",
    "Radiobiological optimizerA radiobiological optimizer will be added to the model to personalize and optimize our TDT model based on the radiobiological properties.",
    "This module captures radiobiological data, such as radiosensitivity, repair, and proliferation capacities using lab tests or other measurements, and RPT can be personalized using this module.",
